cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques to remove undesired reflections from images taken through glass. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves optimization techniques, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of Discrete Cosine Transform for solving the partial differential equation could also relate to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
